{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Sequence_03_9.gif?t=1736369389\" />Aeon Wars Tactics is a multiplayer turn-based strategy, tactical wargame. Featuring true digital miniatures, it is set in an original sci-fi universe where you battle with your friends in epic diorama-style terrains. Collect, build, and customize your army. Engage with your friends in large scale battles and deadly skirmishes. Deploy powerful mechs, special units and unique characters to save humanity or end its dominance on Leng. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_images_combat_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_miniatures_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />Wargaming without real world limits. Aeon Wars brings fully animated handcrafted miniatures, immersive maps with epic diorama-style terrains and a frictionless hobby experience. Your miniatures have never looked so cool!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_custo_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_customize_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />From the smallest of detail on your model to an entire map, everything is customizable in Aeon Wars. Access professional tools to mod, paint and personalize your model to your wildest dreams. Change the cosmetics, weapon loadouts and accessories of your troops to your taste and playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_images_army_builder_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_your_army_SteamRez_v2.png?t=1736369389\" />Assemble your squads to build the perfect roosters for the maps and scenarios you want to play and the strategies you're aiming for. Bring your troops to battle, tweak your loadouts and improve your army until you crush all your enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_images_warfare_steam_rez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_deep_tactical_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />Aeon wars is all about tactical choices. Strategically position your troops on the battlefield, take advantage of covers, run to capture critical objectives and use each of your units unique abilities to secure victory!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_faction_selection_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_choose_faction_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />Decide which faction shall rule and impose its dominion on Leng. Each one has its radically unique flavor and gameplay style. Choose your favorite or try them all to experience the wide variety of models and abilities available to you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_images_universe_SteamRez_v2.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_fight_future_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />It is the year 2411 and what will later be known as the 3rd Aeon War has erupted on Leng, a colonized moon 14 light years away from Earth. Three major fronts collide: the human dominated Nesuv Empire, the corrupted aeons from the Arkosys organization and Pax Terra, the forces from Earth. Will humanity\u2019s traditions be enough to prevent it\u2019s purge by sentient machines? Shall it need to ascend to a new state of being to save itself?</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1939280?t=1736369389","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/1939280?t=1736369389","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736369389","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736369389","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Join our Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Sequence_03_9.gif?t=1736369389\" />Aeon Wars Tactics is a multiplayer turn-based strategy, tactical wargame. Featuring true digital miniatures, it is set in an original sci-fi universe where you battle with your friends in epic diorama-style terrains. Collect, build, and customize your army. Engage with your friends in large scale battles and deadly skirmishes. Deploy powerful mechs, special units and unique characters to save humanity or end its dominance on Leng. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_images_combat_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_miniatures_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />Wargaming without real world limits. Aeon Wars brings fully animated handcrafted miniatures, immersive maps with epic diorama-style terrains and a frictionless hobby experience. Your miniatures have never looked so cool!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_custo_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_page_header_texts_customize_SteamRez.png?t=1736369389\" />From the smallest of detail on your model to an entire map, everything is customizable in Aeon Wars. Access professional tools to mod, paint and personalize your model to your wildest dreams. Change the cosmetics, weapon loadouts and accessories of your troops to your taste and playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1939280/extras/Steam_about_game_